            "description": "In San Antonio, Wytec International, known as WYTC on the OTCQB, has secured a Bridge Loan Facility amounting to $1.65 million. This funding will support the company's efforts in advancing its \"sales agenda\" related to the TXShare multi-government Contract. Wytec aims to boost exposure for its publicly traded shares and accelerate the implementation of its Integrated Public Safety Solution (IPSS) through a Channel Partner Program targeting TXShare Members.",
